These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, scooter, quad-bike, airplane
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, lily, bellflower, dahlia
City: boston, edinburgh, london, nizza
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, light-blue, fuchsia, azure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
4 different pets are kept: frog, snake, pony, rat
 1. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is between the owner of the frog and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
10. the owner of the frog is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who growsdahlia##2
11. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the person who likes azure is the person traveling to nizza##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person traveling to london##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Transport      | airplane        | scooter       | quad-bike  | bike |
| Flower          | dahlia     | bellflower         | lily     | amaryllis    |
| City         | edinburgh  | boston      | london   | nizza     |
| Color           | light-blue | ebony | fuchsia   | azure     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Pet         | rat     | frog     | snake  | pony       |

