 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is between the person drinking almond-milk and the teacher##2
 5. the person who likes white is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 8. the teacher is between the person who's sport is soccer and the tiparillo-smoker##2
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes white is the person who's sport is rowing##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
13. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the pilot##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

